# Chess Game - Platform Independent Distribution

A cross-platform Chess game built with Java and JavaFX, featuring native installers for Windows, macOS, and Linux.

## Table of Contents
- [Features](#features)
- [Prerequisites](#prerequisites)
- [Building the Application](#building-the-application)
- [Platform-Specific Builds](#platform-specific-builds)
- [Running the Application](#running-the-application)
- [Troubleshooting](#troubleshooting)

## Features
- Cross-platform support (Windows, macOS, Linux)
- Native installer generation
- Bundled Java runtime (no separate JRE installation required)
- Desktop shortcuts and menu integration

## Prerequisites

### All Platforms
- JDK 17 or higher
- Apache Maven 3.6+
- Git (optional, for cloning)

### Platform-Specific Tools

#### Windows
- WiX Toolset 3.11+ (for MSI installer)
- Add WiX to system PATH

#### macOS
- Xcode Command Line Tools
- Valid Apple Developer certificate (for signed apps)

#### Linux
- DEB systems: `dpkg-dev`, `fakeroot`
- RPM systems: `rpm-build`

## Building the Application

### 1. Clone the Repository
```bash
git clone <repository-url>
cd chess-game
```

### 2. Build the Shaded JAR
```bash
mvn clean package
```

### 3. Generate Platform Installers

#### Build All Platforms (from respective OS)
```bash
mvn clean install
```

#### Build Specific Platform

**Windows:**
```bash
mvn clean install -P windows
```

**macOS:**
```bash
mvn clean install -P macos
```

**Linux DEB:**
```bash
mvn clean install -P linux-deb
```

**Linux RPM:**
```bash
mvn clean install -P linux-rpm
```

## Maven Configuration

### Complete pom.xml Plugin Configuration

```xml
<plugin>
    <groupId>org.panteleyev</groupId>
    <artifactId>jpackage-maven-plugin</artifactId>
    <version>1.7.1</version>
    <executions>
        <!-- Windows MSI -->
        <execution>
            <id>jpackage-windows</id>
            <phase>install</phase>
            <goals><goal>jpackage</goal></goals>
            <configuration>
                <appName>ChessGame</appName>
                <appVersion>1.0</appVersion>
                <vendor>Org.Example Development</vendor>
                <icon>${project.basedir}/src/main/resources/icon.ico</icon>
                <input>${project.build.directory}</input>
                <mainJar>${project.artifactId}-${project.version}-shaded.jar</mainJar>
                <mainClass>org.example.ChessGame</mainClass>
                <type>MSI</type>
                <runtimeProvided>false</runtimeProvided>
                <destination>${user.home}/Desktop/installer</destination>
                <winDirChooser>true</winDirChooser>
                <winShortcut>true</winShortcut>
                <winMenu>true</winMenu>
                <winMenuGroup>Games</winMenuGroup>
                <addModules>
                    <addModule>java.desktop</addModule>
                </addModules>
            </configuration>
        </execution>

        <!-- macOS DMG -->
        <execution>
            <id>jpackage-mac</id>
            <phase>install</phase>
            <goals><goal>jpackage</goal></goals>
            <configuration>
                <appName>ChessGame</appName>
                <appVersion>1.0</appVersion>
                <vendor>Org.Example Development</vendor>
                <icon>${project.basedir}/src/main/resources/icon.icns</icon>
                <input>${project.build.directory}</input>
                <mainJar>${project.artifactId}-${project.version}-shaded.jar</mainJar>
                <mainClass>org.example.ChessGame</mainClass>
                <type>DMG</type>
                <runtimeProvided>false</runtimeProvided>
                <destination>${user.home}/Desktop/installer</destination>
                <addModules>
                    <addModule>java.desktop</addModule>
                </addModules>
            </configuration>
        </execution>

        <!-- Linux DEB -->
        <execution>
            <id>jpackage-linux-deb</id>
            <phase>install</phase>
            <goals><goal>jpackage</goal></goals>
            <configuration>
                <appName>ChessGame</appName>
                <appVersion>1.0</appVersion>
                <vendor>Org.Example Development</vendor>
                <icon>${project.basedir}/src/main/resources/icon.png</icon>
                <input>${project.build.directory}</input>
                <mainJar>${project.artifactId}-${project.version}-shaded.jar</mainJar>
                <mainClass>org.example.ChessGame</mainClass>
                <type>DEB</type>
                <runtimeProvided>false</runtimeProvided>
                <destination>${user.home}/Desktop/installer</destination>
                <linuxShortcut>true</linuxShortcut>
                <linuxPackageName>chessgame</linuxPackageName>
                <linuxDebMaintainer>sarkaranurag556@gmail.com</linuxDebMaintainer>
                <linuxAppCategory>Game</linuxAppCategory>
                <linuxMenuGroup>Games</linuxMenuGroup>
                <addModules>
                    <addModule>java.desktop</addModule>
                </addModules>
            </configuration>
        </execution>

        <!-- Linux RPM -->
        <execution>
            <id>jpackage-linux-rpm</id>
            <phase>install</phase>
            <goals><goal>jpackage</goal></goals>
            <configuration>
                <appName>ChessGame</appName>
                <appVersion>1.0</appVersion>
                <vendor>Org.Example Development</vendor>
                <icon>${project.basedir}/src/main/resources/icon.png</icon>
                <input>${project.build.directory}</input>
                <mainJar>${project.artifactId}-${project.version}-shaded.jar</mainJar>
                <mainClass>org.example.ChessGame</mainClass>
                <type>RPM</type>
                <runtimeProvided>false</runtimeProvided>
                <destination>${user.home}/Desktop/installer</destination>
                <linuxShortcut>true</linuxShortcut>
                <linuxPackageName>chessgame</linuxPackageName>
                <linuxRpmLicenseType>MIT</linuxRpmLicenseType>
                <linuxAppCategory>Game</linuxAppCategory>
                <linuxMenuGroup>Games</linuxMenuGroup>
                <addModules>
                    <addModule>java.desktop</addModule>
                </addModules>
            </configuration>
        </execution>
    </executions>
</plugin>
```

### Maven Profiles (Optional)

Add to your pom.xml for selective builds:

```xml
<profiles>
    <profile>
        <id>windows</id>
        <activation>
            <os><family>windows</family></os>
        </activation>
        <!-- Windows-specific configuration -->
    </profile>
    
    <profile>
        <id>macos</id>
        <activation>
            <os><family>mac</family></os>
        </activation>
        <!-- macOS-specific configuration -->
    </profile>
    
    <profile>
        <id>linux-deb</id>
        <activation>
            <os><family>unix</family></os>
        </activation>
        <!-- Linux DEB configuration -->
    </profile>
    
    <profile>
        <id>linux-rpm</id>
        <!-- Linux RPM configuration -->
    </profile>
</profiles>
```

## Icon Requirements

Place platform-specific icons in `src/main/resources/`:

- **Windows**: `icon.ico` (256x256, 128x128, 64x64, 48x48, 32x32, 16x16)
- **macOS**: `icon.icns` (1024x1024 recommended)
- **Linux**: `icon.png` (512x512 recommended)

## Installation

### Windows
1. Locate `ChessGame-1.0.msi` in `~/Desktop/installer`
2. Double-click to run installer
3. Follow installation wizard
4. Launch from Start Menu or Desktop shortcut

### macOS
1. Locate `ChessGame-1.0.dmg` in `~/Desktop/installer`
2. Double-click to mount
3. Drag ChessGame.app to Applications folder
4. Launch from Applications or Launchpad

### Linux (DEB)
```bash
sudo dpkg -i ~/Desktop/installer/chessgame_1.0_amd64.deb
```

### Linux (RPM)
```bash
sudo rpm -i ~/Desktop/installer/chessgame-1.0.rpm
```

## Troubleshooting

### Common Issues

**Build fails with "jpackage not found"**
- Ensure JDK 17+ is installed (jpackage included since JDK 14)
- Verify JAVA_HOME points to correct JDK

**Windows: "WiX Toolset not found"**
- Install WiX from https://wixtoolset.org/
- Add WiX bin directory to PATH

**macOS: "Code signing failed"**
- For development: Skip signing with `--mac-sign false`
- For distribution: Obtain Apple Developer certificate

**Linux: "dpkg-dev not found"**
```bash
sudo apt-get install dpkg-dev fakeroot
```

**Icon not appearing**
- Verify icon format matches platform requirements
- Check icon file path in pom.xml

